high_descs: Turn to your left and go to then end of the counter on your right.
Pick up the butter knife on the left edge of the counter.
Turn around and go to the table across from you.
Cut the potato to the left of the cup into slices.
Turn to your left and walk through the kitchen, to the refrigerator on your right.
Place the knife on the shelf, in front of the tomato, in the refrigerator.
Turn to your right and go to the table in front of you.
Pick up one of the potato slices from the table.
Turn to your left and walk through the kitchen, back to the refrigerator on your right.
Place the potato behind the knife, on the second shelf, in the refrigerator, wait a moment for the potato slice to chill, then remove the potato slice from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go to the sink on your right.
Place the potato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold potato slice in the sink.
